                        <p>Easily manage your plant inventory, track growth, and monitor health status.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature-box">
                        <div class="feature-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-tasks"></i>
                        </div>
